As we progress along the spiritual pathwe meet with the tests of
ourapprenticeship. Before each stepforward there is always the testingtime.
When it arrives, if we do notfalter, and, above all, do not think thatit is
evil, or that we have donesomething wrong, or that we aresuffering from an
injustice, we find it isall good.
